WEBVTT

00:05.255 --> 00:08.291
- Here. Take my picture.
- Why?

00:08.425 --> 00:12.672
Happy thoughts. For my beautiful,
young friend. I love you, sweetie.

00:12.804 --> 00:15.377
- What are you doing?
- Piggy-back ride.

00:15.515 --> 00:17.971
Rube said we can't go where they're going.

00:18.101 --> 00:22.051
Open door's an invitation.
Gotta jump while the door's open!

00:27.235 --> 00:32.478
Why do I keep losing all the things
and people that I care about?

00:32.615 --> 00:34.573
Reapers come and go. That's life.

00:34.701 --> 00:36.693
It's Daisy. Daisy Adair.

00:36.828 --> 00:39.663
- Daisy's a reaper.
- I'll call you Georgia.

00:39.789 --> 00:43.075
I hated her instantly.

00:44.419 --> 00:46.744
I hated her a little less.

00:46.880 --> 00:51.209
I died during the making of
Gone With The Wind. I am an actress.

00:51.343 --> 00:54.842
- You miss your sister?
- I was told there would be cookies.

00:54.971 --> 00:57.925
You pick when I'm stressed
to get into this shit.

00:58.058 --> 01:01.473
- Reggie's principal called.
- She's been cutting school?

01:01.603 --> 01:04.010
- Seems so.
- Where the hell's she going?

